            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-700);">~62,846 (2020 Census)</td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 style="color: var(--navy); font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px;">How to Get a Bail Bond in Garfield County</h2>
        <ol style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; font-size: 0.9rem;">
          <li style="display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 14px;">
