      <p style="color: var(--slate-600); font-size: 0.92rem; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 14px;">Garfield County is within our regular service area. In many cases, we can complete the entire bail bond process over the phone — you provide the inmate's information and payment, and we handle the rest directly with the Garfield County Detention Center. For Garfield County bonds, call Angel Bail Bonds at (405) 614-3000 at any hour. Se habla español.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section style="padding: 40px 1.5rem; background: var(--slate-50);">
    <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <h2 style="color: var(--navy); font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px;">Garfield County Bail Bonds FAQ</h2>
      <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px;">
        <details style="background: white; border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px 18px; cursor: pointer; border: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
          <summary style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--slate-800);">How do I bail someone out of the Garfield County Detention Center in Enid?</summary>
          <p style="color: var(--slate-500); margin-top: 10px; font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.6;">Call Angel Bail Bonds at (405) 614-3000 any time, day or night. We handle Garfield County bonds and can coordinate posting with the detention center. The Garfield County Detention Center is at 1020 S 10th St, Enid, OK 73701. Direct jail phone: (580) 548-2429. Once we post the bond, most releases take 2-6 hours.</p>
        </details>
        <details style="background: white; border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px 18px; cursor: pointer; border: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
          <summary style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--slate-800);">How much does a bail bond cost in Garfield County?</summary>
          <p style="color: var(--slate-500); margin-top: 10px; font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.6;">Oklahoma bail bond premiums are regulated by state law. Angel Bail Bonds offers competitive rates with multiple payment options: cash, Visa, Mastercard, Zelle, Venmo, and financing for qualifying clients. Call us at (405) 614-3000 for a free quote on any Garfield County bond.</p>
        </details>
        <details style="background: white; border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px 18px; cursor: pointer; border: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
          <summary style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--slate-800);">How long does release from the Garfield County Detention Center take?</summary>
          <p style="color: var(--slate-500); margin-top: 10px; font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.6;">After Angel Bail Bonds posts the bond, most defendants are released from the Garfield County Detention Center within 2-6 hours. The facility has a capacity of 204 inmates, and processing times depend on current occupancy, staffing levels, and time of day. We work to expedite every release.</p>
        </details>
        <details style="background: white; border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px 18px; cursor: pointer; border: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
          <summary style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--slate-800);">Where is the Garfield County Courthouse?</summary>
          <p style="color: var(--slate-500); margin-top: 10px; font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.6;">The Garfield County Courthouse is at 114 W Broadway Ave, Enid, OK 73701. Open Monday–Friday, 8:00 AM–4:30 PM. Court Clerk phone: (580) 237-0232. For docket and arraignment schedules, contact the clerk or visit oscn.net.</p>
        </details>
        <details style="background: white; border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px 18px; cursor: pointer; border: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
          <summary style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--slate-800);">Can I post bail from Stillwater for a Garfield County arrest?</summary>
          <p style="color: var(--slate-500); margin-top: 10px; font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.6;">Yes. Angel Bail Bonds is based in Stillwater, approximately 65 miles from the Garfield County Detention Center in Enid. We can handle the entire process remotely by phone. You provide the inmate details and payment, and we coordinate directly with the jail to post the bond.</p>
        </details>
        <details style="background: white; border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px 18px; cursor: pointer; border: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
          <summary style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--slate-800);">Does Angel Bail Bonds serve Covington, Drummond, and Waukomis?</summary>
          <p style="color: var(--slate-500); margin-top: 10px; font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.6;">Yes. We serve every community in Garfield County, including Enid, Covington, Drummond, Lahoma, Waukomis, Hunter, Garber, Kremlin, Carrier, Hillsdale, Fairmont, Douglas, Breckinridge, and North Enid. Anyone arrested within Garfield County is booked at the Garfield County Detention Center in Enid.</p>
        </details>
        <details style="background: white; border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px 18px; cursor: pointer; border: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
          <summary style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--slate-800);">What payment methods are accepted for Garfield County bail bonds?</summary>
          <p style="color: var(--slate-500); margin-top: 10px; font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.6;">Angel Bail Bonds accepts cash, Visa, Mastercard, Zelle, and Venmo. We also offer financing plans for clients who qualify. Our goal is to remove financial barriers so your loved one can be released from the Garfield County Detention Center as quickly as possible. Call (405) 614-3000 to discuss payment options.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- NEIGHBORING COUNTIES -->
  <section style="padding: 24px 1.5rem 0; background: white;">
    <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--slate-400); font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin-bottom: 8px;">Neighboring Counties We Serve</p>
      <div style="display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <a href="/noble-county-bail-bonds" style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--blue); text-decoration: none; padding: 6px 14px; background: var(--slate-50); border: 1px solid var(--slate-100); border-radius: 6px;">Noble County →</a>
        <a href="/kay-county-bail-bonds" style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--blue); text-decoration: none; padding: 6px 14px; background: var(--slate-50); border: 1px solid var(--slate-100); border-radius: 6px;">Kay County →</a>
        <a href="/logan-county-bail-bonds" style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--blue); text-decoration: none; padding: 6px 14px; background: var(--slate-50); border: 1px solid var(--slate-100); border-radius: 6px;">Logan County →</a>
        <a href="/payne-county-jail-bail-bonds" style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--blue); text-decoration: none; padding: 6px 14px; background: var(--slate-50); border: 1px solid var(--slate-100); border-radius: 6px;">Payne County →</a>
